data.description: *VA ASSUMABLE LOAN 3.125%*  Unique opportunity to enjoy this beautiful home in a quaint country setting with over 2.5 acres of land. There are covered porches, a large deck an amazing pool and a barn! The interior boast gorgeous hardwoods, tile and a soaring ceiling in the family room with stone fireplace. The owners suite is on the main level. Second level has loft overlooking the family room, 3 additional bedrooms and a bonus room.
